<cu-custom bgColor="bg-gradual-blue" isBack="{{true}}">
  <view slot="backText">返回</view>
  <view slot="content">推广返现</view>
</cu-custom>

<view class="main">
  <view class="title">加入佣金推广计划</view>
  <input class="input" placeholder-class="place-input" maxlength="8" bindinput="bindKeyInput" placeholder="请输入您的真实姓名" />
  <button class="btn" type="primary" open-type="{{openType}}" bindgetphonenumber="getPhoneNumber" bind:tap="joinPlan">
    加入推广计划
  </button>
  <view class="tip">
    <view>tip:</view>
    <view>1.为了后续佣金的提现，需进行实名制!</view>
    <view>2.请输入真实的姓名，避免提现失败!</view>
    <view>3.请授权您的手机号，用于后续的提现!</view>
    <view>4.上述内容暂时无法修改，请保持准确!</view>
  </view>
</view>